A '''rogir-boln''' was a type of fruit native to the planet [[Zonama Sekot/Legends|Zonama Sekot]]. The fruit was harvested, turned into a white paste and eaten by the [[Ferroan]]s. [[Senshi]] grew them on his plantation.

